
1 - Criar pasta "angular7"

mkdir angular7

<b>Instalar Angular 7.3.9</b>

npm install @angular/cli@7.3.9

</b>1ยบ Aula</b>

<b>Criar projeto Angular</b>

ng new exemplos-aula01


<b>Criar componente</b>

ng generate component components/addPessoa
OU
ng g c components/addPessoa

Atividades:

a) ng g c componente01

b) ng g c string-interpolation

c) ng g c property-binding

